<title>USA: M.G. Products Inc Q2 loss widens.</title>
<headline>M.G. Products Inc Q2 loss widens.</headline>
<dateline>SAN ANTONIO 1996-08-20</dateline>
<text>
<p>1996			1995</p>
<p> Shr loss		   $0.30     loss	 $0.16</p>
<p> Net loss		   3,100     loss	 1,400</p>
<p> Revs			 4,400		    6,800</p>
<p> Avg shrs		  10,564		    8,832</p>
<p>(All data above 000s except per share numbers)</p>
<p>NOTE: 1996 Q2 includes a charge of $800,000 for elimination of the company's in-store service group, relocation of distribution center and settlement of a lawsuit with a former employee.</p>
<p>1996 Q2 also includes charges of $700,000 for excess production and overhead costs and $700,000 from inventory writedowns.</p>
